1:47:03.250 --> 1:47:05.540
So Mrs Baker's letting you stay,
is she?

1:47:05.625 --> 1:47:07.999
She told you that, did she?

1:47:08.750 --> 1:47:11.540
"Out of the kindness
of her Christian heart "

1:47:14.375 --> 1:47:18.082
The truth is, Mr Page

1:47:18.166 --> 1:47:22.332
the truth is she says she won't
tell the priest about my Albert

1:47:22.416 --> 1:47:26.790
as long as I work here for nothing

1:47:29.333 --> 1:47:33.040
But they are going to take him
away from me

1:47:33.916 --> 1:47:35.999
You know they will

1:47:40.458 --> 1:47:43.707
And they will throw me out
on to the street

1:47:47.125 --> 1:47:50.165
It's just a matter of time

1:47:53.625 --> 1:47:55.707
Well now

1:47:57.333 --> 1:48:00.874
we can't let that happen, can we?
